        <updateDate>2019-05-28T18:16:35Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Gambling Addiction Prevention Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense (DOD) to: (1) incorporate medical screening questions specific to gambling disorder into the Annual Periodic Health Assessment conducted by DOD for members of the Armed Forces; (2) incorporate into ongoing DOD research efforts questions on gambling disorder; and (3) develop and implement policies and programs on prevention, education, and treatment of gambling disorder and integrate&nbsp;gambling disorder&nbsp;into existing mental health and substance use disorder programs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Gambling Addiction Prevention Act</title>
